<text evidence="5 6 7 8">Interacts with UBTF and the RNA polymerase I complex. Interacts with components of the B-WICH complex, such as MYBBP1A, SMARCA5/SNF2H and BAZ1B/WSTF. Interacts with ELK4, leading to stabilization at target promoters for H3K18Ac deacetylation. Interacts with histone H2A and/or histone H2B.</text>
</comment>
